{
  "text": "This section presents our age-oriented collector. Full details (including pseudocode) are omitted for lack of space, and appear in our technical report [CITATION_1] . Our age-oriented collector extends the reference counting collector of [CITATION_2] by using it for the old generation and adding a tracing collection for the young generation. The tracing collection is in the spirit of the tracing collector in [CITATION_3] .",
  "correct_citation": {
